        "sourceIdentifier": "cve@mitre.org",
        "vendorComments": [
          {
            "comment": "This issue did not affect the version of the Linux kernel as shipped with Red Hat Enterprise Linux 3, as it does not implement the sysfs file system (&quot;/sys/&quot;), through which poll_mode_io file is exposed by the megaraid_sas driver.\n\nIssue was addressed in Red Hat Enterprise Linux 4, 5 and Red Hat Enterprise MRG via https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2010-0076.html , https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2010-0046.html and https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2009-1635.html respectively.",
            "lastModified": "2010-02-04T00:00:00",
            "organization": "Red Hat"
          }
        ],
